</li><li class="c-issue-toc__article c-issue-toc__article--no-translation" data-aricle-no="01">
	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="365"><a href="/en/archive/2018/20-demusealization/art-as-an-agent-of-modernization">Art as an Agent of Modernization: Władysław Strzemiński’s Double Politics of Social Change, the Museum, and Artistic Culture</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Autorzy:--><a href="/pl/bio?id=366">Tomasz Załuski</a></h5>
	
			<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi365" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary365" data-lexicon-show="pokaż" data-lexicon-hide="ukryj">
